;人物的勝利台詞  **MUGEN 1.0 1.1以上版本專用**
;會優先取代畫面包設定的winquote.text勝利台詞，默認語言必須為英語
;每種語言最多可以有100個勝利台詞 (victory0 - victory99)
[Quotes];勝利所說的話 (英文)
victory1 = "We really did think of you as friends!"
victory2 = "Humanity's\nGreatest enemy."
victory3 = "Stupid Humanity......\nNo Hope!"
victory4 = "Titan Win!"

